WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 3=

02:09.460 --> 02:11.700
(He must've killed many,)

02:12.550 --> 02:14.950
(even more than these warriors.)

02:15.830 --> 02:16.852
Since when did the General

02:16.863 --> 02:17.990
become so formidable?

02:19.180 --> 02:21.070
These moves are so unfamiliar.

02:21.620 --> 02:22.860
I've never seen him use them.

02:26.390 --> 02:27.230
How Strange.

02:27.420 --> 02:29.300
This is absolutely bizarre.

02:39.620 --> 02:40.580
Xiaoxiao,

02:40.810 --> 02:41.670
the General wouldn't

02:41.670 --> 02:42.670
have noticed us, right?

02:43.620 --> 02:44.460
He wouldn't.

02:45.390 --> 02:46.670
What is going on?

02:54.390 --> 02:55.230
Commandant Wu,

02:55.230 --> 02:56.606
you think the nobles from Nandu

02:56.617 --> 02:57.900
are just idling their days away.

02:58.580 --> 02:59.700
(The gap between those two)

02:59.700 --> 03:01.110
(is too wide.)

03:01.110 --> 03:02.550
Judging from his experience...

03:03.140 --> 03:04.180
But I'm not one of them.

03:04.180 --> 03:05.790
He could never have such skills.

03:06.070 --> 03:07.700
I know you've never respected me.

03:08.550 --> 03:09.496
Back on the battlefield,

03:10.233 --> 03:11.580
you never made things hard for me.

03:11.580 --> 03:13.140
Where did he learn that?

03:14.420 --> 03:15.740
But now, we face a formidable foe.

03:16.350 --> 03:17.830
You understand the stakes here.

03:18.450 --> 03:19.300
You were displeased

03:19.300 --> 03:20.306
with my strict discipline

03:21.350 --> 03:22.790
because you care for your men

03:24.140 --> 03:25.486
and thought I was being too harsh.

03:25.950 --> 03:26.860
But Commandant Wu,

03:27.300 --> 03:28.909
you know the gap

03:28.920 --> 03:30.049
between the foe and us.

03:31.110 --> 03:32.230
Without strict discipline,

03:33.900 --> 03:35.270
they'll only die faster.

03:39.620 --> 03:41.020
A win is a win.

03:41.420 --> 03:43.070
Cut the nonsense.

03:44.070 --> 03:45.390
I am outmatched.

03:45.790 --> 03:46.630
I accept my defeat.

03:47.110 --> 03:48.070
You can promote

03:48.070 --> 03:49.390
whoever you want.

03:50.990 --> 03:51.830
Commandant Xia,

03:52.790 --> 03:54.740
thank Commandant Wu

03:54.816 --> 03:56.230
and Captain Han for their blessing.

03:57.950 --> 03:58.950
Thank you, Commandant Wu,

03:59.620 --> 04:00.620
Captain Han.

04:03.230 --> 04:04.070
Alright.

04:04.550 --> 04:05.860
If there's nothing else,

04:06.550 --> 04:07.390
I'll take my leave.

04:09.230 --> 04:10.180
Please wait.

04:10.180 --> 04:17.700
(Strict Enforcement)

04:18.030 --> 04:19.500
We are all here today.

04:19.750 --> 04:20.590
Gentlemen,

04:20.600 --> 04:21.953
will you share this drink with me,

04:22.230 --> 04:23.500
so we may retake Yuzhou one day?

04:28.060 --> 04:29.030
Yuzhou?

04:31.260 --> 04:32.260
60 years ago,

04:32.820 --> 04:34.790
North Chong invaded the north.

04:35.590 --> 04:36.710
Heaven is ruthless;

04:37.230 --> 04:38.336
the Guanhe River is frozen.

04:39.180 --> 04:40.559
The North Chong Army marches south,

04:40.790 --> 04:41.676
burning and pillaging,

04:41.820 --> 04:43.183
taking both Yuzhou and Liangzhou.

04:44.550 --> 04:45.860
Though we've retaken Liangzhou,

04:46.380 --> 04:47.860
the people of Yuzhou and the north

04:48.590 --> 04:50.150
still suffer under their cruel rule,

04:50.150 --> 04:51.063
struggling to survive.

04:53.670 --> 04:54.510
Commandant Wu,

04:54.740 --> 04:55.860
will you join me

04:57.616 --> 04:59.049
to save the people from this misery?

04:59.590 --> 05:01.110
Is this the real reason

05:01.110 --> 05:02.060
you called me here?

05:02.380 --> 05:03.470
If I hadn't spread the rumor

05:03.470 --> 05:04.590
about the promotion,

05:05.260 --> 05:06.590
would you fight by my side

05:07.710 --> 05:09.260
with your high standards?

05:15.030 --> 05:15.870
Alright.

05:17.740 --> 05:18.620
Then let's prove it

05:19.620 --> 05:21.420
on the battlefield.

05:23.820 --> 05:24.660
Xiaoxiao,

05:24.790 --> 05:26.260
why am I getting so excited?

05:29.590 --> 05:30.500
Then I should send you

05:30.500 --> 05:31.500
to become a general.

05:31.820 --> 05:32.660
Really?

05:41.150 --> 05:42.060
Never mind.

05:44.990 --> 05:45.830
Why?

05:46.970 --> 05:47.820
Because I want

05:47.820 --> 05:49.060
to always stay with you.

06:03.380 --> 06:04.300
Xu,

06:04.300 --> 06:05.140
your martial arts...

06:05.150 --> 06:06.060
Just a past encounter.

06:11.780 --> 06:13.940
(Grace Upon the Masses)

06:20.740 --> 06:21.580
Strange.

06:22.030 --> 06:23.503
Seed shells are falling from the sky?

06:36.220 --> 06:43.700
(Liangzhou Government Office)

06:43.700 --> 06:44.820
(Liang)

06:44.820 --> 06:45.660
Captain Meng.

06:47.620 --> 06:48.460
What is it?

06:49.300 --> 06:50.300
I didn't know the General

06:50.300 --> 06:51.470
would promote me beforehand.

06:52.150 --> 06:53.790
I thought he valued you more.

07:00.790 --> 07:02.150
Is a Great Liang Commandant

07:02.350 --> 07:03.590
so weak?

07:22.300 --> 07:23.180
You see?

07:23.180 --> 07:24.380
This is the real Xia Qingsheng.

07:24.670 --> 07:26.030
And the true Commandant Xia.

07:26.380 --> 07:28.740
But you were hurt saving me before.

07:29.110 --> 07:30.620
That was a personal matter.

07:32.500 --> 07:33.600
I can't beat you in battle.

07:33.611 --> 07:34.580
That's official business.

07:34.590 --> 07:35.973
Personal and official must not mix.

07:37.620 --> 07:38.740
But you'd better be careful.

07:39.060 --> 07:40.670
I'll catch up to you soon.

07:41.790 --> 07:43.740
After all, you're the only one

07:43.910 --> 07:45.380
I don't dislike other than Xu.

07:51.980 --> 07:55.740
(7th day of the 11th month)

07:55.740 --> 07:58.500
(Liang)

08:02.620 --> 08:04.860
A true man bears his blade

08:04.860 --> 08:07.420
to defend this land until he dies!

08:09.150 --> 08:11.380
A true man bears his blade

08:11.380 --> 08:13.940
to defend this land until he dies!

08:18.820 --> 08:20.500
The General is truly bold

08:21.820 --> 08:23.260
to send 70% of the troops

08:23.260 --> 08:24.420
to attack Yuzhou.

08:25.780 --> 08:28.980
(Guanhe River)

09:16.260 --> 09:17.350
By now,

09:17.900 --> 09:19.780
they should've crossed the river.

09:20.260 --> 09:21.140
Once they cross

09:21.140 --> 09:22.230
the Guanhe River,

09:22.620 --> 09:24.110
does it mean we have won?

09:25.990 --> 09:27.230
Who told you crossing the river

09:27.230 --> 09:28.230
means victory?

09:30.990 --> 09:31.830
One day,

09:32.540 --> 09:33.600
I want to be

09:33.611 --> 09:34.477
just like the General,

09:34.946 --> 09:36.295
so I can fight on the battlefield,

09:36.380 --> 09:37.260
protect our country,

09:38.830 --> 09:39.740
and avenge my father.

09:42.830 --> 09:44.140
Do you want to follow Duan Xu?

09:45.500 --> 09:47.500
I've looked around the city.

09:48.020 --> 09:49.430
Everyone is struggling.

09:49.750 --> 09:50.740
There aren't any families

09:50.740 --> 09:51.730
worth entrusting you to.

09:52.110 --> 09:53.430
Duan Xu isn't a bad choice.

09:54.620 --> 09:56.780
I helped him read the wind.

09:57.350 --> 09:58.470
I can ask him to take you in.

09:59.500 --> 10:00.830
His family is prominent.

10:01.340 --> 10:02.190
If you follow him,

10:02.190 --> 10:03.110
you'll never go hungry.

10:03.500 --> 10:05.190
You might even earn an official title.

10:11.620 --> 10:12.660
Xiaoxiao,

10:12.990 --> 10:14.590
are you abandoning me?

10:14.780 --> 10:16.620
I just want to stay with you.

10:16.620 --> 10:18.900
I can eat less.

10:18.900 --> 10:20.350
I don't need any fruits

10:20.350 --> 10:21.470
or snacks.

10:21.740 --> 10:22.740
That won't do.

10:23.540 --> 10:25.110
As I told you from the start,

10:25.110 --> 10:26.710
I'll only take care of you for a while.

10:28.190 --> 10:29.249
(We walk different paths.)

10:29.570 --> 10:31.380
(You can't follow a spirit forever.)

10:34.950 --> 10:35.790
Besides,

10:36.430 --> 10:38.230
do you think
you can just follow Duan Xu?

10:39.140 --> 10:40.590
He might just die in Shuozhou

10:40.590 --> 10:41.470
and never come back.

10:44.620 --> 10:45.460
Xiaoxiao,

10:45.740 --> 10:47.500
the General is a good man.

10:48.230 --> 10:50.020
Please don't let him die.

10:55.310 --> 10:56.740
You just reminded me.

10:58.380 --> 10:59.220
(This time,)

10:59.220 --> 11:00.710
(Duan Xu will surely die.)

11:01.310 --> 11:02.830
(Then I can get the Deliverance.)

11:03.710 --> 11:04.900
(I have always been fair.)

11:05.500 --> 11:07.070
(So, I won't take it for nothing.)

11:07.710 --> 11:08.550
Xiaoxiao,

11:08.950 --> 11:09.990
you're so powerful

11:10.140 --> 11:11.110
and can do magic tricks.

11:11.710 --> 11:12.950
Please save the General!

11:12.950 --> 11:13.790
Please?

11:14.190 --> 11:15.030
Save him?

11:17.380 --> 11:18.220
Alright.

11:18.950 --> 11:20.165
I'll use the highest standard

11:20.176 --> 11:21.860
in my hometown to save him.

11:23.310 --> 11:25.310
When we spoke with the neighbors,

11:25.460 --> 11:26.050
they said

11:26.061 --> 11:27.570
the only musician here had passed away.

11:28.020 --> 11:28.860
His widow

11:30.470 --> 11:31.310
is named...

11:31.710 --> 11:32.656
What was her name again?

11:33.540 --> 11:34.900
Ms. Song.

11:35.080 --> 11:36.660
Yes, invite her over for melon seeds

11:36.950 --> 11:37.950
and ask her

11:37.950 --> 11:38.790
to bring their Ruan.

11:40.260 --> 11:41.100
Go then.

12:02.430 --> 12:03.270
Enemies!

12:25.260 --> 12:26.620
Light the signal fire!

13:28.660 --> 13:29.710
(Spirit Aura, ascend.)

13:31.540 --> 13:32.380
(Go.)

13:40.260 --> 13:41.350
Foxy,

13:42.070 --> 13:43.350
since you're the rare

13:43.350 --> 13:45.230
Deliverance master in 300 years,

13:46.310 --> 13:47.710
I'll grant you a tune.

13:54.350 --> 13:55.190
Fengyi,

13:55.780 --> 13:56.620
what is it?

13:56.950 --> 13:58.070
Surely, I'll report

13:58.070 --> 13:58.990
the situation to you.

13:59.660 --> 14:00.740
Duan Xu deserves

14:00.740 --> 14:02.430
to be the Deliverance master.

14:03.260 --> 14:04.830
He's been renowned for his talent.

14:04.830 --> 14:05.830
He has an eidetic memory.

14:06.430 --> 14:07.590
At the age of 12,

14:07.780 --> 14:09.660
he was sent to serve his grandmother.

14:10.110 --> 14:10.950
During that time,

14:11.140 --> 14:12.660
his essays often circulated

14:12.860 --> 14:14.866
(Scholars must focus)
and were famous in Daizhou.

14:15.430 --> 14:16.310
But compared to that,

14:17.190 --> 14:18.950
I found something unusual.

14:21.260 --> 14:22.230
When he was 19,

14:22.590 --> 14:24.590
on his way back to Nandu from Daizhou,

14:25.110 --> 14:26.430
he encountered bandits.

14:26.900 --> 14:29.070
His attendants and servants

14:29.070 --> 14:30.540
were all killed.

14:30.540 --> 14:32.430
He alone survived

14:44.190 --> 14:46.140
and trekked all the way to Nandu.

14:46.310 --> 14:47.260
Since then,

14:47.260 --> 14:49.020
he's settled down in Nandu.

14:50.470 --> 14:52.380
Coincidentally,

14:53.260 --> 14:56.500
shortly after he returned to Nandu,

14:56.660 --> 14:58.470
his grandmother passed away.

14:59.190 --> 15:01.430
So, all the people he knew

15:01.430 --> 15:02.780
over the seven years in Daizhou

15:03.110 --> 15:04.710
are all gone?

15:05.230 --> 15:06.660
Yes, interesting, isn't it?

15:07.110 --> 15:08.500
For a 19-year-old scholar

15:08.500 --> 15:09.340
like him,

15:09.470 --> 15:11.380
how could he single-handedly

15:11.380 --> 15:12.830
fight off a gang of bandits?

15:13.380 --> 15:14.220
Perhaps

15:15.430 --> 15:16.310
the real Duan Xu

15:16.310 --> 15:17.590
died alongside his servants

15:17.590 --> 15:19.830
at the age of 19.

15:26.900 --> 15:28.780
(From 12 to 19)

15:28.780 --> 15:31.190
(is when a mortal child
changes the most.)

15:33.020 --> 15:33.900
(During this time,)

15:33.900 --> 15:35.660
(even if he was replaced
by someone else,)

15:36.380 --> 15:38.260
(no one would necessarily notice.)

15:50.430 --> 15:51.350
(I found you,)

15:54.310 --> 15:55.380
(Duan Xu.)

16:04.350 --> 16:05.500
You are a spent force.

16:06.380 --> 16:07.740
Just a dying struggle.

16:08.900 --> 16:10.950
I don't even need to strike you myself.

16:12.020 --> 16:13.900
Let me play a dirge for you.

16:57.500 --> 16:58.860
A cornered beast still fights.

17:03.020 --> 17:04.060
Interesting.

17:04.990 --> 17:07.500
Let me see how long you can hold out.

17:20.770 --> 17:21.630
General!

17:21.630 --> 17:22.470
Xu!

18:45.950 --> 18:47.300
You asked me to read the wind.

18:47.580 --> 18:49.190
Aren't you crossing the river

18:49.390 --> 18:50.390
to attack Shuozhou?

18:50.740 --> 18:51.820
Must you go?

18:51.820 --> 18:53.100
Only by seeking peace

18:53.300 --> 18:54.390
through battle

18:54.390 --> 18:55.230
can Great Liang

18:55.240 --> 18:56.870
and North Chong lay down their arms

18:57.780 --> 18:58.630
and embrace peace.

19:00.390 --> 19:01.710
This is my deepest wish.

19:02.230 --> 19:03.070
If possible,

19:04.430 --> 19:05.740
please help me achieve it.

19:17.190 --> 19:18.190
In four days,

19:18.580 --> 19:19.740
on the 8th of the 11th month,

19:22.630 --> 19:23.820
east wind at You hour.

19:24.500 --> 19:26.420
(Liang)

19:59.950 --> 20:01.990
Red birds are to burn all living beings.

20:02.230 --> 20:04.820
Red birds are to burn all living beings.

20:07.020 --> 20:08.780
Attack!

20:10.710 --> 20:12.990
Fire arrows!

20:13.340 --> 20:14.630
Fire arrows!

20:50.990 --> 20:55.060
Attack!

20:55.060 --> 20:55.990
Reinforcements are here!

20:56.470 --> 20:58.190
Our reinforcements are here!

20:58.340 --> 20:59.910
Reinforcements are here!

21:00.190 --> 21:01.260
Attack!

21:01.500 --> 21:03.870
Attack! Attack!

21:03.870 --> 21:05.100
Attack!

21:05.260 --> 21:09.780
Attack! Attack!

21:10.190 --> 21:12.710
Attack! Attack!

21:12.990 --> 21:13.870
Red birds are to burn

21:14.670 --> 21:15.710
all living beings.

21:17.150 --> 21:18.020
Red birds are to burn

21:18.820 --> 21:19.870
all living beings.

21:21.190 --> 21:22.630
Authentic Chong language.

21:25.020 --> 21:25.910
Red birds are to burn

21:26.710 --> 21:27.740
all living beings.

21:29.060 --> 21:31.100
He's surely not the old Duan Xu.

21:35.489 --> 21:37.059
(Born into a family of civil officials,)

21:37.070 --> 21:38.540
(you possess superb martial arts;)

21:39.150 --> 21:40.470
(aiming to be a Chief Councillor,)

21:40.470 --> 21:42.100
(you speak fluent Chong language.)

21:42.470 --> 21:43.536
(You claim to be Duan Xu,)

21:44.020 --> 21:45.670
(but those
who could prove your identity)

21:45.670 --> 21:47.230
(are long dead.)

21:47.580 --> 21:49.820
(How many secrets are you hiding?)

21:51.190 --> 21:52.580
The battle is won.

21:55.820 --> 21:56.990
It seems

21:56.990 --> 21:57.910
I'll have to wait

21:58.230 --> 21:59.630
to play the dirge for Foxy.

22:04.990 --> 22:07.910
Red birds are to burn all living beings.

22:08.470 --> 22:09.990
Red birds are to burn

22:10.670 --> 22:12.300
all living beings.

22:18.780 --> 22:20.230
Red birds are to burn...

22:25.820 --> 22:27.190
Things are getting interesting.

22:32.740 --> 22:35.100
Perhaps letting you live in this world

22:36.300 --> 22:37.870
would be more entertaining.

23:06.540 --> 23:07.820
Great victory in Shuozhou!

23:08.056 --> 23:09.605
The Tabai Army crosses the Guanhe River

23:09.616 --> 23:10.820
for the first time in 30 years!

23:11.100 --> 23:12.430
Great victory in Shuozhou!

23:12.670 --> 23:14.230
The Tabai Army crosses the Guanhe River

23:14.230 --> 23:15.470
for the first time in 30 years!

23:15.470 --> 23:16.670
We crossed the Guanhe River!

23:16.670 --> 23:17.870
The Great Liang Army won!

23:18.260 --> 23:19.430
We won! We won!

23:19.789 --> 23:20.945
(Honor the Worthy)
Xiaoxiao!

23:20.990 --> 23:22.150
The General won!

23:22.300 --> 23:23.910
We've taken Shuozhou City!

23:24.540 --> 23:25.380
Xiaoxiao!

23:25.950 --> 23:26.870
Xiaoxiao!

23:27.020 --> 23:27.910
Xiaoxiao!

23:28.190 --> 23:29.390
The General won!

23:29.950 --> 23:30.820
Xiaoxiao!

23:32.780 --> 23:33.670
Xiaoxiao!

23:35.740 --> 23:36.580
Xiaoxiao!

23:37.260 --> 23:38.190
The General won!

23:38.470 --> 23:39.740
We've taken Shuozhou City!

23:40.150 --> 23:41.470
- Xiaoxiao!
- Alright, I get it.

23:41.710 --> 23:42.630
Also, Xiaoxiao,

23:42.829 --> 23:44.378
the General sent someone to pick us up!

23:44.430 --> 23:45.270
Let's go now.

23:59.870 --> 24:01.500
Captain Han Lingqiu of the Tabai Army

24:01.910 --> 24:03.020
requests to see Miss He.

24:04.140 --> 24:09.850
(Liangzhou Government Office)

24:09.870 --> 24:10.710
Miss He,

24:11.430 --> 24:12.763
the General has a message for you.

24:13.190 --> 24:14.260
Shuozhou has fallen.

24:14.780 --> 24:16.660
Your insight from the wind
contributed greatly.

24:17.100 --> 24:17.940
Thus,

24:18.150 --> 24:18.990
he humbly asks you

24:18.990 --> 24:20.230
to keep reading the wind for us

24:20.430 --> 24:21.270
and head to Shuozhou.

24:23.540 --> 24:25.390
The General knows you are delicate

24:25.670 --> 24:27.540
and averse to bloodshed
and worldly affairs.

24:28.230 --> 24:29.100
He promises

24:29.430 --> 24:30.476
to spare you from hardship

24:30.710 --> 24:31.670
and ensure your safety.

24:31.670 --> 24:32.580
He won't force you.

24:33.060 --> 24:33.990
What do you think?

24:35.540 --> 24:36.580
Foxy,

24:37.150 --> 24:38.390
you're quite clever

24:38.580 --> 24:39.740
to know my likes and dislikes.

24:42.300 --> 24:43.630
Since the General invited me,

24:43.630 --> 24:44.870
I'd be honored to accept.

24:45.500 --> 24:47.100
I'll go pack our bags.

24:50.990 --> 24:52.230
Since you want to play,

24:52.670 --> 24:54.260
I'm happy to oblige.

24:56.860 --> 25:00.420
(Shuozhou City)

25:03.100 --> 25:04.340
- Be quick.
- Yes, General.

25:04.340 --> 25:05.540
The supplies the enemy left

25:05.540 --> 25:06.580
have all been confiscated.

25:06.910 --> 25:08.363
Inventory and add them to the armory.

25:09.100 --> 25:09.990
And set aside a portion

25:10.430 --> 25:11.340
for the citizens.

25:12.263 --> 25:13.699
The captive citizens of Great Liang

25:13.710 --> 25:14.670
must be registered

25:15.150 --> 25:15.990
and properly settled.

25:16.340 --> 25:17.180
Yes.

25:23.010 --> 25:23.850
Slow down.

25:25.060 --> 25:25.900
Xu,

25:26.390 --> 25:27.430
by now,

25:27.560 --> 25:28.156
Captain Han

25:28.167 --> 25:29.260
should've reached Liangzhou

25:29.260 --> 25:30.150
and picked up Miss He.

25:33.060 --> 25:34.100
They should've met by now.

25:34.470 --> 25:35.910
Captain Han is acting suspiciously.

25:36.340 --> 25:37.950
If he really is a spy,

25:38.230 --> 25:39.430
wouldn't Miss He be in danger?

25:51.670 --> 25:52.540
Xiaoxiao,

25:52.700 --> 25:53.689
it seems we've reached

25:53.700 --> 25:55.230
North Chong's occupied territory.

25:58.910 --> 25:59.750
Xiaoxiao,

26:00.060 --> 26:01.470
what is that pattern?

26:02.910 --> 26:04.150
Flame pattern.

26:04.430 --> 26:05.820
The symbol of North Chong.

26:11.190 --> 26:12.030
What's wrong?

26:12.430 --> 26:13.270
Feeling unwell?

26:15.540 --> 26:16.670
Xiaoxiao,

26:17.020 --> 26:17.990
my grandfather said

26:18.710 --> 26:21.060
our ancestral home was in Shuozhou.

26:22.260 --> 26:24.100
When he was still alive,

26:24.710 --> 26:26.150
North Chong attacked us.

26:27.230 --> 26:28.910
He took our whole family

26:29.150 --> 26:30.580
and fled south to Liangzhou.

26:31.910 --> 26:33.340
At that time, we had

26:34.230 --> 26:35.340
no home or food.

26:36.190 --> 26:37.390
My grandfather said

26:37.870 --> 26:39.260
that in his lifetime,

26:39.630 --> 26:40.990
and even in mine,

26:41.820 --> 26:43.500
we might never return to Shuozhou.

26:45.300 --> 26:46.820
But today, I've returned.

26:54.780 --> 26:56.710
I want to travel even further.

27:00.470 --> 27:02.300
(How pitiful of mortals.)

27:02.633 --> 27:04.190
(The journey of their entire lifetime)

27:04.190 --> 27:05.240
(is but a mere few steps.)

27:14.390 --> 27:15.230
Mr. Lin,

27:15.630 --> 27:16.856
thanks for letting me stay here

27:16.990 --> 27:18.020
these past few days.

27:19.300 --> 27:20.430
No need to be so polite.

27:21.500 --> 27:22.563
We, the people of Shuozhou,

27:22.574 --> 27:23.958
have longed for Great Liang's army

27:23.969 --> 27:24.870
for 30 years.

27:25.580 --> 27:27.660
(Lin Jun, Shuozhou merchant)
We hope

27:27.670 --> 27:29.500
to be Great Liang citizens again.

27:29.706 --> 27:30.952
- General Duan.
- General Duan.

27:32.670 --> 27:33.510
These two gentlemen

27:33.670 --> 27:35.230
are members of the Shuozhou guild.

27:35.820 --> 27:36.660
They came today

27:37.390 --> 27:38.740
to represent the guild

27:39.340 --> 27:40.780
and the people of the city

27:41.100 --> 27:42.340
to ask you a question.

27:42.710 --> 27:43.910
Please speak freely.

27:44.470 --> 27:45.310
Then,

27:45.630 --> 27:46.650
I'll be completely frank.

27:47.630 --> 27:49.710
You took over Shuozhou this time

27:50.100 --> 27:51.390
through a surprise attack.

27:51.990 --> 27:53.370
Now, you're surrounded by enemies.

27:53.990 --> 27:56.100
If the citizens welcome you now

27:56.670 --> 27:58.710
and become slaves to North Chong again,

27:59.150 --> 28:00.950
they'll surely be slaughtered
out of anger.

28:01.820 --> 28:04.020
Liangzhou's tragedy will repeat itself.

28:05.150 --> 28:06.500
So, I want to ask you:

28:07.230 --> 28:08.340
How long do you plan

28:09.230 --> 28:10.340
to stay this time?

28:12.190 --> 28:14.580
How long will you protect its people?

28:21.540 --> 28:22.500
Rest assured, everyone.

28:23.100 --> 28:23.940
For 30 years,

28:24.496 --> 28:26.209
Great Liang never forgot
Shuozhou's people.

28:26.670 --> 28:28.740
The Tabai Army has crossed the river,

28:29.283 --> 28:30.740
and we won't take a single step back.

28:31.150 --> 28:32.856
We'll live and die
with Shuozhou's people.

28:34.390 --> 28:35.910
We know defending the city is hard.

28:36.500 --> 28:37.580
Since you've decided

28:37.580 --> 28:39.430
to protect the people of this city,

28:40.580 --> 28:43.100
we will certainly do our utmost

28:43.580 --> 28:44.740
without any hesitation.

28:45.740 --> 28:47.470
We too will do our utmost

28:47.670 --> 28:48.630
without any hesitation.

28:51.060 --> 28:51.900
It has been 30 years.

28:52.990 --> 28:54.870
We finally crossed the river again.

28:55.447 --> 28:57.000
North Chong held Shuozhou
for 30 years.

28:57.540 --> 28:58.390
We took it suddenly,

28:58.390 --> 28:59.580
so they won't just let it go.

29:00.046 --> 29:01.260
Their Fenglai Force is watching

29:01.260 --> 29:02.253
from Yuzhou in the south.

29:02.500 --> 29:03.430
Awo'erqi is leading

29:03.430 --> 29:04.500
200,000 soldiers

29:04.500 --> 29:05.630
right toward us.

29:05.780 --> 29:07.060
Our troops are now exhausted;

29:07.430 --> 29:08.390
we are short on rations.

29:08.670 --> 29:10.163
The city's people refuse to cooperate.

29:10.670 --> 29:11.780
Can we still hold the city?

29:15.910 --> 29:16.750
We must.

29:17.820 --> 29:18.660
For 30 years,

29:19.190 --> 29:20.185
the people of Great Liang

29:20.196 --> 29:21.630
were enslaved and slaughtered

29:22.430 --> 29:23.270
by North Chong.

29:23.740 --> 29:25.213
It's not that they reject our rescue.

29:26.020 --> 29:26.950
They are just terrified.

29:27.470 --> 29:28.710
They fear this slim hope

29:28.710 --> 29:29.710
is just fleeting.

29:30.910 --> 29:31.750
So, we must protect

29:33.260 --> 29:34.740
this hope for them.

30:06.820 --> 30:08.950
Ambush! Ambush!

30:08.950 --> 30:09.790
On guard!

30:30.540 --> 30:31.380
Hold them off!

30:48.060 --> 30:49.910
Xiaoxiao!

30:51.210 --> 30:52.060
Are we there yet?

30:52.060 --> 30:53.470
An ambush by North Chong.

31:02.300 --> 31:03.540
They have at least 200 men.

31:03.910 --> 31:05.060
We only have a few dozen.

31:05.580 --> 31:06.950
We're doomed this time.

31:08.150 --> 31:10.020
Will the General come save us?

31:11.470 --> 31:12.950
We're still far from Shuozhou.

31:13.390 --> 31:15.060
He's too far to help.

31:15.870 --> 31:17.340
If we're caught,

31:17.800 --> 31:19.100
I'll just read the wind for them.

31:19.340 --> 31:20.390
I'm reading it anyway,

31:20.390 --> 31:21.330
no matter who it's for.

31:21.540 --> 31:22.380
Right?

31:25.580 --> 31:27.300
You'll help them?

31:28.340 --> 31:29.462
They drove my grandfather

31:29.473 --> 31:30.710
from Shuozhou to Liangzhou

31:30.990 --> 31:32.470
and killed my father in Liangzhou.

31:32.910 --> 31:33.750
Why is it always them

31:33.760 --> 31:34.740
bullying us?

31:35.060 --> 31:36.820
And you'll help them?

31:37.060 --> 31:38.670
I'd rather die than help them!

31:44.060 --> 31:45.710
A remote path like this

31:45.710 --> 31:47.100
shouldn't have so many ambushers.

31:50.060 --> 31:51.300
Foxy,

31:53.150 --> 31:54.780
I knew getting on your carriage

31:54.780 --> 31:55.990
would mean trouble.

32:05.400 --> 32:06.260
Miss He!

32:06.260 --> 32:07.710
It's dangerous! Please go inside!

32:07.710 --> 32:08.550
On guard!

32:11.540 --> 32:12.380
On guard!

32:33.240 --> 32:38.570
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

32:38.900 --> 32:43.150
♪Light encountered shadow♪

32:44.510 --> 32:49.880
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

32:50.180 --> 32:54.780
♪The unbreakable fate♪

32:55.870 --> 32:57.710
♪Suddenly cracked♪

33:09.920 --> 33:15.360
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

33:15.540 --> 33:19.870
♪Light encountered shadow♪

33:21.240 --> 33:26.630
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

33:26.860 --> 33:30.800
♪The unbreakable fate♪

33:32.570 --> 33:34.460
♪Suddenly cracked♪

33:37.120 --> 33:40.280
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

33:40.280 --> 33:42.810
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

33:42.810 --> 33:48.330
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

33:48.330 --> 33:51.570
♪Following fate's guidance♪

33:51.570 --> 33:56.430
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

33:56.770 --> 33:59.790
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

33:59.790 --> 34:02.610
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

34:02.870 --> 34:05.400
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

34:05.400 --> 34:10.820
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

34:10.990 --> 34:14.060
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

34:14.220 --> 34:19.120
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

34:19.330 --> 34:22.800
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
